What you need to know:

At Vet Lab Sports Club, Paresh Shah combined 17 and 24 for 41 points to win the Dr Fernando Wangila Memorial tournament, where the men’s prize went to Charles Kamari with 40 points after beating Kamlesh Shah on countback.The ladies title went to Wambui Okello on 40 points, winning well ahead of Jane Mwangi on 35 points. In the guest category, P. Njunge emerged the winner with a score of 35 points. 